OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FThe former chief executive of Southern
OL,7,FWater has been charged with conspiracy
OL,8,Fto defraud authorities over
OL,9,Fallegations he was involved in a plan
OL,10,Fto manipulate water quality tests to
OL,11,Favoid millions of pounds in penalties.
OL,13,FMatthew Wright has been accused
OL,14,Falongside three others of conspiring
OL,15,Fto defraud the Environment Agency (EA)
OL,16,Fand water regulator Ofwat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FThe EA previously asked a judge to
OL,7,Fissue a summons against Wright, as
OL,8,Fwell as Philip Barker, Clive Massey
OL,9,Fand Mark Gregory, who also worked at
OL,10,Fthe company, charging them with the
OL,11,Foffence.The summons was issued last
OL,12,Fyear, but Wright then launched a legal
OL,13,Fchallenge over the move, with his
OL,14,Flawyers telling the High Court in June
OL,15,Fthat the EA did not have the power to
OL,16,Fissue it and that it should be thrown
OL,17,Fout as a "nullity".
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, two senior judges
OL,7,Fdismissed Wright's claim, and ruled
OL,8,Fthat restrictions previously
OL,9,Fpreventing reporting of the legal
OL,10,Fchallenge should be lifted.
OL,12,FSeparate court listings show that the
OL,13,Fcase against 60-year-old Wright, of
OL,14,FHaslemere in Surrey, Barker, 57, of
OL,15,FChiltington in West Sussex, 64-year-
OL,16,Fold Massey, of Brandhill, Shropshire,
OL,17,Fand 63-year-old Gregory, from
OL,18,FSouthampton, were scheduled to be
OL,19,Fheard at Medway Magistrates' Court on
OL,20,FJuly 14.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FThe four are accused of conspiring
OL,7,Fbetween 2012 and 2017 to "defraud
OL,8,Fpersons performing public duties in
OL,9,Frespect of environmental and financial
OL,10,Fregulation" of Southern Water,
OL,11,Fincluding the EA and Ofwat, by "the
OL,12,Fimplementation of artificial no-flow
OL,13,Fevents at waste water treatment works".
OL,15,FThe court listings also show that
OL,16,FSouthern Water has separately been
OL,17,Fcharged with dozens of offences of
OL,18,Ffailing to comply with or contravening
OL,19,Fan environmental permit condition
OL,20,Fbetween 2013 and 2017 at multiple
OL,21,Fwastewater treatment works.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUrD@KO]sD@`OUuD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FWastewater treatment works can only be
OL,7,Frun with an environmental permit
OL,8,Fissued by the EA.
OL,10,FTreated effluent discharge from the
OL,11,Fworks is tested under an "operator
OL,12,Fself-monitoring" (OSM) scheme
OL,13,Fintroduced in 2009, which sees
OL,14,Fdischarges tested annually in
OL,15,Funannounced visits.
OL,17,FThe tests are carried out by sampling
OL,18,Fteams, which operate separately from
OL,19,Fteams that run the works.
OL,26,@sD@ZOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FThe results of the tests are shared
OL,7,Fwith the EA and water regulator Ofwat,
OL,8,Fand can lead to penalties if the works
OL,9,Fdo not comply with the terms of their
OL,10,Fpermits.
OL,12,FIf the discharge flow at the time of
OL,13,Fthe test is insufficient to take a
OL,14,Fsample, this is not regarded as a
OL,15,Ffail, and no samples are taken for the
OL,16,Frest of the testing period.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FRules around OSM have been tightened
OL,7,Fin the past year, including that
OL,8,Fsamples must be rescheduled in the
OL,9,Fevent that the flow is insufficient,
OL,10,Fwith the current Labour government
OL,11,Fpledging to end the practice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FIn his ruling issuing the summons
OL,7,Fagainst the four men last year,
OL,8,FDistrict Judge Stephen Leake said:
OL,9,F"The agency alleges, in the present
OL,10,Fcase, that there was a deliberate plan
OL,11,Fby officers of the company to
OL,12,Fmanipulate the OSM regime by
OL,13,Fcontriving operational circumstances
OL,14,Fso that there was no flow through the
OL,15,Frelevant site at times when it was
OL,16,Fbelieved that the site would, or
OL,17,Fmight, fail the OSM test, in order to
OL,18,Favoid the consequences of the true OSM
OL,19,Fresult being provided to the agency
OL,20,Fand Ofwat."
OL,26,@qD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FBut lawyers for Wright told the High
OL,7,FCourt that the EA only has the power
OL,8,Fto bring private prosecutions for
OL,9,Fenvironmental offences, not those such
OL,10,Fas fraud or conspiracy.Barristers for
OL,11,Fthe EA said that the body had a
OL,12,Fgeneral power to bring private
OL,13,Fprosecutions, and alternatively that
OL,14,Fallegations of conspiracy to defraud
OL,15,Fwere connected to its
OL,16,Ffunctions.Massey, Gregory and Barker
OL,17,Fdid not appear at the hearing in
OL,18,FLondon and were not represented.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FLord Justice Popplewell, sitting with
OL,7,FMr Justice Hilliard, ruled on
OL,8,FWednesday that the EA only being able
OL,9,Fto prosecute environmental offences
OL,10,Fwould "produce unreasonable and
OL,11,Fanomalous results".
OL,13,FHe continued that the law "enables the
OL,14,FEA to prosecute for any offence of any
OL,15,Fnature in circumstances in which such
OL,16,Fa prosecution is capable of being
OL,17,Fcalculated to facilitate, or conducive
OL,18,For incidental to, the carrying out of
OL,19,Fany of its functions".
OL,26,@rD@GOUsD@RO]uD@[OU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,FIn the 48-page judgment, the senior
OL,7,Fjudge continued that the charge
OL,8,Fagainst Wright involves "very serious
OL,9,Fallegations of criminal misconduct".
OL,11,FHe said: "What is alleged ... involves
OL,12,Fcarefully planned and extensive fraud
OL,13,Fand dishonesty at a high level within
OL,14,Fthe company and on a large scale,
OL,15,Fincluding, for example, arranging for
OL,16,Fwastewater to be removed from
OL,17,Ffacilities by tankers in order to
OL,18,Fcreate no flow results, with a view to
OL,19,Fcovering up pollution and deceiving
OL,20,Fthose whose function is to protect the
OL,21,Fpublic from such harm.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@cO]sD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,F"The EA says that by the company's own
OL,7,Fassessment, it avoided penalties of
OL,8,Fthe order of #45 million, and on the
OL,9,FEA's assessment the figure is higher."
OL,11,FFollowing the judgment, an EA
OL,12,Fspokesperson said: "We can confirm
OL,13,Fthat we are taking criminal
OL,14,Fproceedings against Southern Water
OL,15,FServices Limited and a number of
OL,16,Fformer employees.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]tD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784735286
OL,3,CEx-Southern Water boss charged with
OL,4,Cconspiracy to defraud over water tests
OL,6,F"We take our responsibility to protect
OL,7,Fthe environment very seriously and
OL,8,Fwill always pursue and prosecute those
OL,9,Falleged to have committed serious
OL,10,Foffending against the environment.
OL,12,F"We welcome this important judgment."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/13
